plication tools and electromechanical devices on december   berkshire hathaway acquired marmon group previously it was a privately held conglomerate owned by the pritzker family for over fifty years which owned and operated an assortment of manufacturing companies that produce railroad tank cars shopping carts plumbing pipes metal fasteners wiring and water treatment products used in residential construction on october   berkshire hathaway automotive an autodealership subsidiary was created through the acquisition of van tuyl group the remaining largest auto dealer in the nation and independentlyowned up to that date and it is the fifth largest with ownership of  dealerships and revenues of  billion on november   berkshire hathaway announced that it would acquire duracell from procter  gamble for  billion in an allstock deal finance and financial productsedit berkshire acquired clayton homes a maker of modular homes storage trailers chassis intermodal piggyback trailers and domestic containers claytons finance business loans to manufactured home owners earned  million down from  million in  loan losses remain  up from  investmentsedit as well as owning companies outright berkshire maintains a concentrated portfolio of equities and investments which has historically been managed by warren buffett since  todd combs and ted weschler also work alongside buffett in managing investments in the  letter to shareholders warren revealed that each of them independently manages greater than  billion on behalf of berkshire buffett has spoken very highly of both in public interviews and in the  letter to shareholders he described hiring them both as one of my best moves as of march   of berkshires equity securities are concentrated in five companies american express company   billion apple inc   billion the cocacola company   billion international business machines corporation “ibm”   billion and wells fargo  company   billion at the peak of the financial crisis in september  berkshire invested  billion in preferred stock in goldman sachs to provide it with a source of funding when capital markets had become constrained the preferred stock yielded an annual interest rate of  earning berkshire  million in interest income per year berkshire also received warrants to purchase  million shares with a strike price of  per share which were exercisable at any time for a five year term goldman maintained the right to purchase back the preferred stock and in march  exercised this right paying  billion to berkshire the preferred stock could only be purchased back at a  premium the warrants have been exercised and berkshire holds  of the share capital of goldman sachs profit on the preferred stock was estimated at  billion and exercising the warrants has yielded a profit of more than  billion berkshire still owns shares in goldman sachs so the entire profit cannot be quantified on august   berkshire hathaway purchased  billion of preferred shares in bank of america the investment has an annual interest cost of  earning berkshire  million in annual interest alongside the preferred stock investment berkshire obtained warrants allowing berkshire to buy  million common shares at  per share any time before september   based on the share price in june  this position has yielded a profit of more than  billion excluding the annual interest earned from the preferred stock vandergriff automotive the highest selling honda dealership in the dallas metroplex contributes  million in revenue every year in  pepsi paid berkshire  million to insure against a contest pepsi held which had a potential  billion prize the prize had a very small chance of being won and it was not won by anyone in  berkshire hathaway inc acquired russell corporation for  million in fact getting most shares and brands in many sports leagues – including spalding nba official basketballs bike athletic company protections aai american athletic gymnastics tables bars rings horses or dudley softball